<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Chief Cornerstone — Landscaping + Full CMS', metaDesc: 'A stunning 5-page landscaping website with a complete business CMS. Client manager, job scheduler, expense tracker, weather alerts, soil data, and more.' }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav', { activePage: 'templates' }) %>

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Chief Cornerstone</h1>
  <p>Landscaping & Lawn Care — Website + Full Business CMS</p>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Hero Preview -->
    <div style="border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.15);margin-bottom:48px">
      <img src="/images/chief-cornerstone.jpg" alt="Chief Cornerstone Template Preview" style="width:100%;display:block">
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 360px;gap:48px;align-items:start">

      <!-- Left: Details -->
      <div>
        <div style="background:#f0f7e8;border-left:4px solid #4CAF50;border-radius:0 10px 10px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:32px;font-size:.95rem;color:#1A2E1A;font-weight:600">
          This is not just a website template — it's a complete business platform built specifically for landscaping companies.
        </div>

        <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:16px">What's Included</h2>

        <h3 style="color:#1A2E1A;margin-bottom:12px;margin-top:24px">🌿 5-Page Public Website</h3>
        <ul style="padding-left:20px;line-height:2;color:#555">
          <li>Home — full-screen sliding hero with 5 photos, services preview, faith statement</li>
          <li>Services — detailed service cards with descriptions</li>
          <li>About — company story, values, scripture</li>
          <li>Gallery — before/after project photos managed from CMS</li>
          <li>Contact — quote request form that feeds straight to your dashboard</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="color:#1A2E1A;margin-bottom:12px;margin-top:28px">📊 Full Business CMS Dashboard</h3>
        <ul style="padding-left:20px;line-height:2;color:#555">
          <li><strong>Client Manager</strong> — add and track every client by name, address, ZIP, and service type</li>
          <li><strong>Job Scheduler</strong> — schedule jobs, track status, log completion and price</li>
          <li><strong>Employee Tracker</strong> — manage your crew, roles, and hourly rates</li>
          <li><strong>Expense Dashboard</strong> — log fuel, equipment, overhead, and labor by category</li>
          <li><strong>Weather by ZIP</strong> — 7-10 day forecasts so you know before a rain day hits your schedule</li>
          <li><strong>Soil Data by Area</strong> — USDA soil type data so you know what you're quoting before you arrive</li>
          <li><strong>Gallery Manager</strong> — upload and manage project photos from the admin panel</li>
          <li><strong>Quote Request Inbox</strong> — every contact form submission goes straight to your dashboard</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="color:#1A2E1A;margin-bottom:12px;margin-top:28px">✅ What Gets Customized For You</h3>
        <ul style="padding-left:20px;line-height:2;color:#555">
          <li>Your business name replaces "Chief Cornerstone"</li>
          <li>Your logo and brand colors</li>
          <li>Your phone number and email</li>
          <li>Your service area and city</li>
          <li>Your own photos in the hero slider and gallery</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="background:#fff8e6;border:2px solid #D4A227;border-radius:12px;padding:24px;margin-top:36px">
          <div style="font-weight:800;color:#8a6200;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px">💡 Why Monthly Instead of One-Time?</div>
          <p style="color:#5a4000;font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.75">Your $99/month includes hosting, updates, support, and new features as they're added — weather alerts, soil data, and more coming. You're not buying a frozen website. You're getting a living business tool that gets better over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Pricing + CTA -->
      <div style="position:sticky;top:24px">
        <div style="background:white;border:2px solid #e8e0d0;border-radius:16px;padding:32px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08)">
          <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:24px">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;font-weight:800;color:#1A2E1A">$99</div>
            <div style="color:#7a7a6a;font-size:.88rem;font-weight:600">/month — includes hosting & support</div>
          </div>

          <ul style="list-style:none;margin-bottom:28px">
            <% [
              '5-page professional website',
              'Full business CMS dashboard',
              'Client & job management',
              'Expense & fuel tracking',
              'Weather alerts by ZIP code',
              'Soil data by area',
              'Gallery & quote management',
              'Hosting included',
              'Updates & support included',
              'No setup fee. No contract.'
            ].forEach(item => { %>
            <li style="padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f5f0e8;font-size:.9rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px">
              <span style="color:#4CAF50;font-weight:700">✓</span> <%= item %>
            </li>
            <% }) %>
          </ul>

          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;padding:16px;font-size:1rem">Get Started Today</a>
          <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:12px;font-size:.8rem;color:#9a9a8a">We'll reach out within 24 hours to get you set up.</div>
        </div>

        <div style="background:#1A2E1A;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin-top:16px;text-align:center">
          <div style="color:#8BC34A;font-style:italic;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.7">"Unless the Lord builds the house, the builders labor in vain."</div>
          <div style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-size:.75rem;margin-top:8px">— Psalm 127:1</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
